bilingual.target: 这是一个成功的音乐会。
她是一位成功的艺术家。

bilingual.source: What made Han Gan a successful painter?
bilingual.target: 什么使韩干成为一名成功的画家？

bilingual.source: I want my child to be a successful person.
bilingual.target: 我希望我的孩子成为一个成功的人。

bilingual.source: When did David become a successful writer?
bilingual.target: 大卫什么时候成为成功的作家？

bilingual.source: We want to know how you've become so successful.
bilingual.target: 我们想知道你是如何变得如此成功的。

bilingual.source: You'll keep on practising and you'll be successful.
bilingual.target: 你会不断练习并且会成功的。

bilingual.source: He became a successful actor and began to write plays.
bilingual.target: 他成为了一名成功的演员并开始写戏剧。

bilingual.source: Garth is one of the most successful musicians in American history.
bilingual.target: 加斯是美国历史上最成功的音乐家之一。

bilingual.source: Well known as a successful band, the Impact members show quite a few striking abilities.
bilingual.target: 作为一个成功的乐队，影响乐队的成员展示了不少惊人的能力。

list.abstract: successful（英 [səkˈsesfl]，美 [səkˈsesfl]），英语单词，形容词，意思为成功的；有成就的；受欢迎的。短语搭配有most successful（最成功；多数成功），例句为“He is successful in fighting cancer.（他成功地战胜了癌症。）” successful形容词类近义词有made、triumphant，相关反义词有unsuccessful，动词形式为succeed，名词形式为success，比较级为more successful，最高级为most successful，副词形式为successfully。

yingyinNormal.en: This is not the normal way of being, but through this approach, I became very successful. And being successful enabled me to meet extraordinarily successful people and see how they think.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是普遍的方法，但我通过它取得了成功。成功让我能遇见更加成功的人，看他们怎么想。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know what you're implying. Oh. Here is my very successful business partner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道你这话是什么意思。这位是我非常成功的生意合作伙伴。

yingyinNormal.en: Having big dreams, plus embracing reality, plus having lots of determination will bring you a successful life. I believe this formula is true for everyone. But what does a successful life look like?
yingyinNormal.zh: 最好的方式有了宏伟的梦想，加上许多的决心肯定会在生活中获得成功。我相信这个办法适用于所有人。但成功的生活是什么样子的？

yingyinNormal.en: Penny was a struggling actress when we met, and now she's a successful pharmaceutical rep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们刚认识时，佩妮是个落魄的小演员，现在她是成功的医药代表。

yingyinNormal.en: Like, you know, he was the more successful one when we started out. No, I didn't know that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如，他是事业上更成功的那一方，当我们开始的时候，我并不知道这个

yingyinNormal.en: She was terrible to me, Kate. Josie, this skinny, successful woman that you admire so much?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她对我很糟糕，凯特。乔茜，这个身材窈窕又成功的女人，你真的那么崇拜她吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm afraid if I take this, I might lose that special, unique something that makes me so successful in my field.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我怕我吃了这个药以后，可能会丧失那些让我在我的领域里如此成功的特质。

yingyinNormal.en: It's classic, though, isn't it? The successful wife. The husband feels like his manhood is threatened, so he acts out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太典型了，对吧。一个成功的妻子，丈夫觉得自己的男子气概受到威胁了，所以他就偷腥去了

yingyinNormal.en: These principles took me from being a very ordinary middle class kid from Long Island to becoming very successful as judged by conventional measures.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些法则让我从一个普通的长岛来的中学小孩变成传统意义上非常成功的人。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm now at a stage in my own life in which it is much more important to me to pass along what I've learned about how to be successful than to seek more success for myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在的生活阶段对我更重要的是，将我所学到的成功的知识传递下去，而不是自己追寻成功。

yingyinNormal.en: A successful life essentially consists of doing these five steps over and over again. This is your personal evolution, and you see this process everywhere. It's just a law of nature.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个成功的生活一般就是这五步不断的重复。这是你的个人发展，你在各处都能看到这些步骤。这是自然法则。

yingyinNormal.en: Any attempt on the director's life had to look successful.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了让人觉得局长真的被谋杀了。

yingyinNormal.en: There was enough altitude and speed after the bird strike for a successful return to LaGuardia. Successful? The plane landed at LaGuardia. Intact. Undamaged.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在鸟击过后，飞机有足够的高度和速度可以成功返回拉瓜迪亚机场。成功返回？飞机降落在拉瓜迪亚机场完好无缺，未有损坏。

yingyinNormal.en: No. I care very much. But I also care about running a successful business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是，我很在意教育的质量，但我更在意的是如何把生意做好。

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard, I had no idea your siblings were so much more successful than you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德，我不知道你兄妹的成就都比你高这么多。

yingyinNormal.en: You could not be more wrong. You could try, but you would not be successful.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你错得不可能再错，你可以试，可是你不会成功。

yingyinNormal.en: Max, this is it. This is our factory. The employees look happy and successful.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麦克斯，就是这里了，我们要的工厂，这里的员工们看起来又开心又成功。

yingyinNormal.en: You will be happy. You will be successful. And you will make a difference in the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 会品味到喜悦与成功，打造出属于自己的一片天地。

yingyinNormal.en: I agree with General Braegher. While a successful air strike against Ahmadi would play well…
yingyinNormal.zh: 我同意布雷格将军的看法。虽然对艾哈迈迪发动精确空袭会非常有利于…

yingyinNormal.en: So, Dr. Hofstadter, Leonard rarely talks about his incredibly successful brother and sister.
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍夫斯塔德博士，莱纳德很少谈及他成就颇高的姐姐和弟弟。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: If the sustainable-egg rollout is <highlight>successful</highlight>, it could open the floodgates for regenerative beef, broccoli, and beyond.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果可持续鸡蛋推广成功，它可能会为再生牛肉、西兰花等打开闸门。

examination_example.sentence: The most <highlight>successful</highlight> monarchies strive to abandon or hide their old aristocratic ways.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最成功的君主政体努力抛弃或隐藏他们古老的贵族生活方式。

examination_example.sentence: In The Prince, he championed cunning, ruthlessness, and boldness, rather than virtue, mercy and justice, as the skills of <highlight>successful</highlight> leaders.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在《君主论》一书中，他将狡猾、无情和勇敢拥为成功领袖所需的技能，而不是美德、仁慈和公正。
